SELECT 
    m.NomMatiereFr AS nom_matiere,
    n.orale,
    n.TP,
    n.ExamenEcrit,
    n.DS,
    n.DC1,
    n.DC2
FROM 
    noteeleveparmatiere n
JOIN 
    matiere m ON n.id_matiere = m.id
WHERE 
    n.id_inscription IN (SELECT id FROM inscriptioneleve WHERE Eleve IN (SELECT id FROM eleve WHERE IdPersonne IN ({id_personne})));
